FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781187095
OL,3,CBen Stokes and Gus Atkinson left out
OL,4,Cby England for second Test against
OL,5,CKiwis
OL,7,FThe ECB said in a statement on
OL,8,FWednesday that the pair had "not been
OL,9,Fmade available for selection".
OL,11,FFormer England captain Joe Root will
OL,12,Flead the side on an interim basis as
OL,13,Fvice-captain.
OL,15,FThe pair remain under investigation by
OL,16,Fthe ECB and the independent Cricket
OL,17,FRegulator.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781187095
OL,3,CBen Stokes and Gus Atkinson left out
OL,4,Cby England for second Test against
OL,5,CKiwis
OL,7,FHowever, fears that Stokes was
OL,8,Fpreparing to step down as captain or
OL,9,Fretire from international cricket have
OL,10,Fcooled.
OL,12,FInstead, the ECB has effectively
OL,13,Fbought itself more time by leaving
OL,14,Fboth players out of next Wednesday's
OL,15,Fsecond Test against New Zealand at the
OL,16,FKia Oval, without taking any formal
OL,17,Fdisciplinary action.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, Harry Brook has not been
OL,20,Fasked to step up from his role as vice-
OL,21,Fcaptain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781187095
OL,3,CBen Stokes and Gus Atkinson left out
OL,4,Cby England for second Test against
OL,5,CKiwis
OL,7,FInstead, the responsibility has gone
OL,8,Fto Root, who served as captain for
OL,9,Ffive years before stepping down in
OL,10,F2022 and is regarded as one of the
OL,11,Fmost experienced figures in the
OL,12,Fdressing room.
OL,14,FBrook has been England's white-ball
OL,15,Fcaptain for more than a year and
OL,16,Freplaced Ollie Pope as Ben Stokes'
OL,17,Fdeputy last summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
