PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781187095
OL,3,CBen Stokes and Gus Atkinson left out
OL,4,Cby England for second Test against
OL,5,CKiwis
OL,7,FBrook was involved in a nightclub
OL,8,Fincident during England's tour of New
OL,9,FZealand in November before the Ashes,
OL,10,Fwhen he was struck by a bouncer
OL,11,Ffollowing a late-night drinking
OL,12,Fsession on the eve of a one-day
OL,13,Finternational in Wellington.
OL,15,FWhile no curfew was in place at the
OL,16,Ftime, Brook was heavily fined, issued
OL,17,Fwith a final warning and sanctioned by
OL,18,Fthe Cricket Regulator.
OL,20,FThis is breaking news, more to
OL,21,Ffollow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
